					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[This Self-Assessment Survey will help you to assess and improve your Quality Management System (QMS).]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="90">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="90" uuid="8870ef96-ebd0-4e00-98ba-1ed53f528853"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[The questions are colour-coded. <font color="#ec6607">Orange</font> criteria are <font color="#ec6607">'shall'</font> criteria, i.e. meeting them is a requirement. <font color="#004280">Blue</font> criteria are <font color="#004280"> 'should'</font> criteria, i.e. meeting them is recommended. Making true and accurate statements will help you get genuine feedback on your Quality Managment System and, as a result, improve certain processes in the future.]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
