				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Does the biobank establish, document, implement and maintain a quality management system that is capable of supporting and demonstrating the consistent achievement of the requirements of relevant QMS standards assuring the quality of biobanking?
<br><font color="#ec6607">shall</font>]]></text>
			</staticText>
